Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.14,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we will do a quick theater today.\N{\rChinese}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:09.28,English,,0,0,0,,Now, as a society, every society has a problem.\N{\rChinese}翻译1”
